data.description: 10.13 rolling acres with a view and privacy. Developers/ Builders/ Single Family/ Families.......Make this your Custom dream home site(s)/ private retreat and more. Come Watch the sunrise and sunset. Roads are cut in with gravel laid,  partially cleared and has Evergreens lining the property.  There is an abundance of wildlife and large parcels of just land adjacent in the back for extra privacy !   The home on the land is approx 1300 sq ft 1bd 1ba with a remodel just waiting to happen.  Loudon County Water and Electric already in place with a septic.  Toqua Golf Course, Tellico Village, Tellico Village Yacht Club, Rarity Bay Golf and Country Club,    Buyers agent and Buyer to verify all information. Pre Approval/Qual to be submitted with all offers.  Offers require a 24hr response time for seller.  Continue reading..... Since 2004: new piles in crawlspace, floor joist, sub-floor, insulation, 2 electrical panels, Hvac, roof, water heater, wood burning stove, gutters, windows, drywall. Home is awaiting your vision for the remodel.
